reviewText: No complaints, it is what I expected.
Multiple episodes from different shows about World War 1 not what I wanted. Just wish they would  of had historian and more vets in it like the revolution dvd set from the history channel.

Classic Documentary of World War 1.  How War advances the means man kills man.  Germany was 1st to use deadly gas.  How air travel before the plane progressed to the daring  Dog Fight. Much original action movies.  Excellent for sincere movie buffs.
I collect historical books and movies and World War I is of particular interest.  Very well done and very accurate.
